## Payment Integration

### Paystack (Visa/Mastercard)
```php
// Initialize payment
$payment->initializePaystackPayment($order_id, $amount, $email, $callback_url);

// Verify payment
$payment->verifyPaystackPayment($reference);
```

### Mobile Money
```php
// Initialize mobile money payment
$payment->initializeMoMoPayment($order_id, $amount, $phone, $network);

// Check payment status
$payment->checkMoMoStatus($reference);
```

